      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>I hear what you're saying, but it feels less like a beginning and more like a conclusion. All these landmarks, all this scenery... it's just beautiful scenery on the way to nothing. It feels like I've reached the end of the map. Like there's no point in planning the next leg of the journey when the destination is just more of the same. Does it ever feel to you like some journeys are just meant to end?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
